room_title: Escape room "Swan Song" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
room_description: Professor Sigmund Hunt has wreaked havoc throughout the world for years, but his time is running out. Infected with the zombie virus at his mysterious lab, it now threatens to overwhelm him. He has retreated back into his mountain estate, but things have . . . changed. Nature has begun to reclaim the space, and as the professor’s mind has degraded, so have his quarters. It is up to you to explore the chaos, sort through the madness, and uncover the fate of Professor Hunt in his “Swan Song”!
